  "Subject": "Your Waitlist Slot is Ready: IIT Madras Tech \u0026 AI Hackathon",
  "Body": "\u003C!DOCTYPE html\u003E\n\u003Chtml\u003E\n\u003Chead\u003E\n    \u003Cstyle\u003E\n        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }\n        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 5px; }\n        .header { background-color: #2b6cb0; color: white; padding: 15px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }\n        .content { padding: 20px; }\n        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #2b6cb0; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 15px; }\n        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }\n    \u003C/style\u003E\n\u003C/head\u003E\n\u003Cbody\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022container\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022header\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Ch2\u003EYour Waitlist Slot is Ready!\u003C/h2\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022content\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Cp\u003EGood news! Tickets have become available for \u003Cstrong\u003E{IIT Madras Tech \u0026 AI Hackathon}\u003C/strong\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\n            \u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETier:\u003C/strong\u003E {VIP Access}\u003C/p\u003E\n            \u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EQuantity:\u003C/strong\u003E {1}\u003C/p\u003E\n            \u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color: #fff3cd; color: #856404; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 15px;\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Cstrong\u003EImportant:\u003C/strong\u003E You have until \u003Cstrong\u003E{Jul 11, 2026 06:31}\u003C/strong\u003E (UTC) to complete your booking. If you do not book by this time, your slot will be offered to the next person on the waitlist.\n            \u003C/div\u003E\n            \u003Ca href=\u0022{http://localhost:4200/booking?eventId=10008}\u0022 class=\u0022button\u0022 style=\u0022color: #ffffff;\u0022\u003EComplete Booking Now\u003C/a\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022footer\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Cp\u003EIf you no longer wish to attend, you can safely ignore this email.\u003C/p\u003E\n            \u003Cp\u003E\u0026copy; 2026 Event Platform. All rights reserved.\u003C/p\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/body\u003E\n\u003C/html\u003E\n"
}